# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Conventional infantry within the DCMS serve as the foundation of planetary defense, providing the manpower essential to territorial control while freeing BattleMech and armored assets for offensive operations. The platoon tows an infantry-portable gauss rifle that uses magnetic acceleration instead of chemical propellant. No muzzle flash, no propellant signature, no risk of ammunition explosion, and the projectile arrives with enough velocity to threaten anything short of assault-weight armor.</p>
</overview>

